# Testing

## File Mirroring
lib/src/features/auth/data/repositories/auth_repository_impl.dart
→ test/unit/features/auth/data/repositories/auth_repository_impl_test.dart

## Unit Tests
- mocktail for all mocks. Never real HTTP, real DB, or real auth in unit tests.
- Every entity, mapper, value object, repository impl must have tests.
- State containers: ProviderContainer with overrides (Riverpod) or fake bindings (GetX).
- Every error path tested: NetworkFailure, AuthFailure, NotFoundFailure minimum.

## Widget Tests
- Pump real widget tree (not just widget in isolation where possible).
- Verify Semantics.identifier targets for interactive elements.
- Test empty state, error state, loading state for all data-fetching views.
- Test PATTERN-002 (double-tap prevention) for every submit button.

## Contract Tests (test/contract/)
- Deserialize REAL API response JSON fixtures → Flutter Freezed models.
- Fail loudly if field names, types, or nullability differ.
- Run on every PR against staging environment fixture snapshots.

## Coverage Gate
- ≥85% line coverage on ALL new files.
- CI fails hard if new file drops below threshold.
- Exclude: *.g.dart, *.freezed.dart, main_*.dart.

## BUG_PATTERNS → TEST_SPEC Integration
- Run /analyze-bugs after every BUG_PATTERNS.md update.
- Every PATTERN must have at least one corresponding SPEC test.
